            <p>We hope this message finds you well. We are writing to inform you that your [Software Name] subscription has expired on [Expiration Date].</p>
            <p>While your software continues to function, it is crucial to note that your subscription has expired, and your access to essential updates and support may be limited.</p>
            <p>Renewing your subscription is highly recommended to ensure you continue to receive the latest features, security updates, and priority support. This will also help maintain the security and performance of your software.</p>
